		 * Format the provide logRecord to string.
		 *
		 * <p>the string format:</p>
		 * <p>[LevelName]    Time message</p>
		 * <p>[DEBUG]    12:02:22 this is debug message</p>
		 * @param logRecord a logRecord.
		 * @return a formated string.
		 */
